snippet.textDisplay: Nas recently addressed his comment about Mike on his Instagram stories. He said that he still considers Mike a good friend, and clarified that what he meant about Mike is that he's not the biggest game player, but the best player of the game. In the sense that Mike is the best survivor, managing to survive a number of dangerous dumping situations by playing his cards right, until he finally met Priscilla. So Nas was trying to compliment Mike's ability to adapt to difficult situations, not trying to shade him. That's what Nas wanted to explain in this video, but the interviewers didn't give him the chance to explain.
